metadata.name: Alpha Woofs
metadata.description: Wonder Woof holders burn 5 Bone NFTs to acquire 1 Alpha Woof and join the exclusive Wolf Pack. The Wolf Pack is a mastermind group with the Founders, this elite group of holders will be the community leaders, entrepreneurs, creators, and visionaries who see and create WONDER IN THE WORLD!  Alpha Woof holders also hold a stake in the Community Wallet where funds from our product sales are deposited.
